&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience in Solidworks or NX, and PLM systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Solid understanding and application of GD&amp;amp;T&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Advanced designing skills for CNC machining, composites, sheet metal, injection molding, PCBA integration&lt;/li&gt;
