&lt;li class=&quot;zfr3Q TYR86d eD0Rn &quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;zfr3Q CDt4Ke &quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;C9DxTc &quot;&gt;We do sponsor and take over sponsorship of employment visas for this role. If we make you an offer, we will make every reasonable effort to get you a visa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
