&lt;div class=&quot;x_x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Pay range: &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Avionics Systems Engineer/Level I: $100,000.00 - $120,000.00/per year &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Avionics Systems Engineer/Level II: $115,000.00 - $135,000.00/per year &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
