&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To conform to U.S. Government export regulations, applicant must be a (i) U.S. citizen or national, (ii) U.S. lawful, permanent resident (aka green card holder), (iii) Refugee under 8 U.S.C. § 1157, or (iv) Asylee under 8 U.S.C. § 1158, or be eligible to obtain the required authorizations from the U.S. Department of State. Learn more about the ITAR &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pmddtc.state.gov/?id=ddtc_kb_article_page&amp;amp;sys_id=24d528fddbfc930044f9ff621f961987&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
