&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or equivalency certificate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ months of experience in a hands-on technical field such as automotive, electronics, or other high-volume manufacturing industry, or&amp;nbsp;an associate’s degree in a STEM field&lt;/li&gt;
